<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>The 12th and final contestant to appear on Strictly Come Dancing 2020 is reportedly YouTube star HRVY.</p>

<p>The 21-year-old is a singer and CBBC presenter, with an album set to be released this November, and The Sun claim he is the mystery 12th star to be unveiled. </p>

<p>HRVY - real name Harvey Leigh Cantwell - will follow in the footsteps of former internet star contestants Joe Sugg and Saffron Barker - the latter of whom is close friends with him.</p>

<p>Rounding things off: The 12th and final contestant to appear on Strictly Come Dancing 2020 is reportedly YouTube star HRVY</p>

<p>The pair have also been linked romantically, with HRVY serenading Saffron on her YouTube channel. The pair have also been on tour together.</p>

<p>The pair have claimed, however, that they are just friends.</p>

<p>HRVY has a following on YouTube of 2.76 million, and 4.6 million Instagram followers. His YouTube videos have been viewed over 500 million times.</p>

